    Page: 601
  Source:
    Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Charity=Love of the Neighbour
---
Arise and accept an antidote to ward off old age and death; it is the knowledge
that all wealth and prosperity, all pleasures and enjoyments are harmful to us
unless devoted to the good of others; they tend only to sicken and enervate our
frames.
